Why Track Polymarket Insiders

Polymarket is a prediction market where people bet real money on real world events.

When someone creates a brand new wallet and places 50000 dollars on a 10 cent outcome, that is a signal worth paying attention to.

Patterns often seen from insiders:

Fresh wallets with massive bets
-> Wallet created hours ago
-> Places a 30000 dollar bet on one outcome

Dormant wallets reactivating
-> Silent for 2 months
-> Suddenly buys 25000 dollars of a low odds position

Clustered timing
-> Multiple new wallets
-> Betting the same direction within minutes

Contrarian conviction
-> Buying heavily below 15 cents
-> Market disagrees

These patterns have preceded major market moves on Polymarket multiple times.

